title: Legend of Stanky Creek TT and XC
Summer Weekday TT Series Part 2 (Lakeland IH Park)
2017 Montgomery Bell Classic TN State Championship
description: Come enjoy some great  Middle Tennessee Singletrack at beautiful Montgomery Bell State Park.  Race your friends and foes head to head on the Time Trial on Saturday and then again on the XC course on Sunday.   The XC course is approx. 9 miles with a mixture of fast flowing singletack, tight twisting singletrack and a few challenging sections thrown in for good measure.  Good field start to thin out the groups before getting into the tight singletrack.  TBRA TN State Championship Race for 2017!
course: Good field start to thin out the groups before getting into the tight singletrack.   9 mile race loop for the Cat 1 and Cat 2 groups.  2 - 4 mile looks for the older juniors and Cat 3.  1 - 4 mile loop for the 9-14 juniors.
registration: Online Registration on USAC discounted before Sept. 1st after that it goes up $5.  Pre-reg closes at noon on the Friday before the race 9/15.  After that the onsite registration is $5 more and closes 15 minutes before each race.
directions: ADDRESS:  830 Bill Duke Road, White Bluff, TN 37187
